        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Support Earned Recognition for Veterans Act or the SERV Act </strong></p> <p>Excludes from the definitions of &quot;active duty,&quot; &quot;active duty for training,&quot; and &quot;inactive duty training,&quot; for veteran benefit or employment preference purposes, any service performed at a preparatory school of a service academy by a student who is not otherwise a member of the Armed Forces.</p>]]></text>
